{"word":"ἐπίσκοπος","slug":"ἐπίσκοπος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἐπίσϰοπος, οῦ, ὁ</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:σκοπός\">σκοπός</a></el>, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐπισκέπτομαι\">ἐπισκέπτομαι</a></el>] ‘one who engages in oversight’, <b>overseer, supervisor,</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> focus on role of guardian in a caring mode<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> of humans <b><a href='B:510 20:28'>Ac 20:28</a>; <a href='B:570 1:1'>Phil 1:1</a>; <a href='B:610 3:2'>1 Ti 3:2</a>; <a href='B:630 1:7'>Tit 1:7</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> of God <b><a href='B:670 2:25'>1 Pt 2:25</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐπισκοπή\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐπισπάομαι\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}